<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/551862-hey-guys-i-am-not-a-native-but-i-m-not">hey guys!
I am not a native, but I&#39;m not new to novels.......
 I cant quite understand the text in this book, 
Am I the only one???
should I read another book prior to this one in ortherto understand???
(the literary books I had read and came across with no problem at all: pride and prejudice, Frankenstein etc,,, )
thanks in advance</a>
</div>
