        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1273822525" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3651368805793543785">I did not end up caring much for this book. I really wanted to like it since it is a classic, but it really was a chore for me. There was so much time jumping without obvious breaks that it was difficult to understand. It also didn&apos;t help that there was a mix of prose, poetry, and stream of consciousness.<br/><br/>I can see how some might see this as a must read, but not me.</span>
  <span id="freeText3651368805793543785" style="display:none">I did not end up caring much for this book. I really wanted to like it since it is a classic, but it really was a chore for me. There was so much time jumping without obvious breaks that it was difficult to understand. It also didn't help that there was a mix of prose, poetry, and stream of consciousness.<br /><br />I can see how some might see this as a must read, but not me.</span>
